月销量甚至不足百辆。 同时，尽管终端车企大幅降价，汽车销量和整体库存水平并未持续提高，价格下探带来的成交转化效果趋弱。其中，价格战“重灾区”自主品牌的库存系数为1.53，‌环比上升了8.5%，是行业内最高。 这种大幅度的降价促销行为，虽然在一定程度上刺激了市场需求，促进了销量的增长，但其背后所隐藏的问题却不容忽视。 首先，价格战的持续进行意味着车企利润空间被不断压缩。为了争夺市场份额，车企不得不采取降价策略来吸引消费者。吉利杨学良：“卷”一日不消，中国汽车不会真正走遍全球_易车"},"attached_info":"CkAIsJSG9/eEprx5EAMaCTEwOTMxNTczMSC9iNO0BjAAOKkCQBNyCTY2MTY3MDU0NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"58 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-10dad3ef7d76b68d6a1cf687676ad005_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"20_1721924392.748293","card_id":"Q_653553525","target":{"id":653553525,"title":"如果皇帝封后宫的一个女人为尿嫔会怎么样？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/653553525","type":"question","created":1713606720,"answer_count":59,"follower_count":90,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[53690,163833,2540698],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IsJSG9/eEprx5EAMaCTEwNzUxMjExMCDAoI6xBjAAOFpAFHIJNjUzNTUzNTI1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"57 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"21_1721924392.748662","card_id":"Q_638922973","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":638922973,"title":"100多米厚的煤层，是怎么形成的？远古地球真有这么多植物吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/638922973","type":"question","created":1704880895,"answer_count":68,"follower_count":162,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1540,3298,13029,23606],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkA